T1  - The Interaction of Job Stress and Social Support: A Strong Inference Investigation
AU  - Seers, Anson
AU  - McGee, Gail W.
AU  - Serey, Timothy T.
AU  - Graen, George B.
Y1  - 1983/06/01
PY  - 1983
DA  - 1983/06/01
