T1  - Turnaround Strategies for Mature Industrial-Product Business Units
AU  - Hambrick, Donald C.
AU  - Schecter, Steven M.
Y1  - 1983/06/01
PY  - 1983
DA  - 1983/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/255972
