T2  - Academy of Management Journal
JF  - Academy of Management Journal
JO  - AMJ
SP  - 231
EP  - 248
VL  - 26
IS  - 2
PB  - Academy of Management
N2  - A study of short-term turnaround attempts by mature industrial-product business units found that efficiency-oriented moves, but not entrepreneurial initiatives, were associated with successful turnaround. Three common types of successful turnaround ?gestalts? were found: asset/cost surgery, selective product/market pruning, and piecemeal moves.
AB  - A study of short-term turnaround attempts by mature industrial-product business units found that efficiency-oriented moves, but not entrepreneurial initiatives, were associated with successful turnaround. Three common types of successful turnaround ?gestalts? were found: asset/cost surgery, selective product/market pruning, and piecemeal moves.
